  m_text: "A fast and powerful predator of the Pacific Ocean, the Pacific Bluefin
    Tuna is built like a living torpedo. It migrates across entire oceans and can
    dive over five-hundred meters deep. Its dark blue back and silver underside help
    it blend into open water while it hunts fish at high speeds reaching up to 70
    km/h. Speed limit? This tuna clearly didn\u2019t read the ocean traffic laws!\r"
