  m_text: "A deep-sea clam that lives buried in soft seafloor sediment near cold
    seeps. Its hard shell\r\nprotects it, while symbiotic bacteria inside its gills
    convert chemicals from the seabed into\r\nnutrients, allowing it to survive in
    the dark ocean depths. Meals are always ready when the chef\r\nlives in your
    gills!\r"
